Module geci.annotation
Package javax0.geci.annotations

Annotation Type Geci

  • @Retention(RUNTIME)
@Repeatable(Gecis.class)
public @interface Geci
    This annotation is used by many code generators that work with Java::Geci. The classes, fields or other Java language elements that the code generators consider to get information from are annotated with this annotation and the parameter provides value for the code genrators.

    For example the setter/getter generator will look at the classes and in case they have a @Geci("accessor ...") annotation it will generate the setters and the getters for the fields of the class. Classes that do not have such an annotation will not be effected by the accessor code generator.

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element Description
      java.lang.String value
